      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8087-bc32-f7ae2760b60e",
        "type": "sub_sub_header",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "帰還者将軍"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123444633,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123568146
      }
    },
    "32c3b07c-81ff-8088-9ba7-df78e1a13d7c": {
      "value": {
        "id": "32c3b07c-81ff-8088-9ba7-df78e1a13d7c",
        "type": "divider",
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1774254591413,
        "last_edited_time": 1774254591978
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8029-b643-ec81daa16a67": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8029-b643-ec81daa16a67",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "崩壊エネルギー指数が臨界点に達すると、死域内に「帰還者将軍」と呼ばれる特殊な存在が現れる。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123443177,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123446188
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8057-86af-fd4a1f350a20": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8057-86af-fd4a1f350a20",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "帰還者将軍を倒せば、活性化した死域を弱め、素早く閉鎖することができる。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123446786,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123454658
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-805f-be0e-f1f29fe9b1b7": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-805f-be0e-f1f29fe9b1b7",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "軍の内戦の前には存在しなかった。カリスマがユカタン大死域を開いた後に現れた。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123556527,
        "last_edited_time": 1768125423946
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8030-9b63-ddff95b47db0": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8030-9b63-ddff95b47db0",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "一定の知性を持つ超高レベルの崩壊エネルギー使い。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123463488,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123555082
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8053-9e50-ebe1021b74d2": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8053-9e50-ebe1021b74d2",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "無限の崩壊エネルギーを放つことができ、その実力は聖痕騎士を上回っている。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123474344,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123476596
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-805c-9827-cd5d1f310201": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-805c-9827-cd5d1f310201",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "討伐には専門の軍を編成することが多い。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123483112,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123484023
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8029-a5c8-c1ae2717a0ff": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8029-a5c8-c1ae2717a0ff",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "空間の裂け目から突如として現れるのが通常。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123493847,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123494748
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8092-a2fa-ef0a5362168c": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8092-a2fa-ef0a5362168c",
        "type": "text",
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123536826,
        "last_edited_time": 1768123536828
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-8096-89c3-fd56c8881c17": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-8096-89c3-fd56c8881c17",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "強力な聖痕使いが崩壊エネルギーに侵食されると、意識が薄れ、内戦の戦場にいると思い込んでしまう。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123510457,
        "last_edited_time": 1768125288013
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-804e-90ef-fbed6c85d825": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-804e-90ef-fbed6c85d825",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "聖痕を使うことが可能。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768123535375,
        "last_edited_time": 1768125392469
      }
    },
    "2e53b07c-81ff-80c8-b474-c61d4a716276": {
      "value": {
        "id": "2e53b07c-81ff-80c8-b474-c61d4a716276",
        "type": "text",
        "properties": {
          "title": [
            [
              "空間の亀裂を開いて、崩壊宇宙に逃げることが可能。"
            ]
          ]
        },
        "parent_id": "1bf3b07c-81ff-80f9-a733-ed6a4f3c1b69",
        "parent_table": "block",
        "created_time": 1768125381212,
        "last_edited_time": 1768125390538
      }
    },
